<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN""http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd"> <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <head> <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/> <title>ReactJS Developer seeking roles in Dreamweaver, Javascript, React.Js, Frontend Development,UI Development,Web Development,Api Integration,Web Designing, Material Ui, Nextjs, Responsive Web Design.</title> </head> <body>   <div style="width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;padding:30px 45px;font-family:'Calibri';color:#7F7F7F;background-color:white"> <div style="width:100%;margin-bottom:25px;padding-bottom: 5px;"> <div> <div style="font-size:1.4em;margin-bottom:3px;font-weight:bold;">Kotha Mahesh Babu</div> <div>  Senior Software Engineer at EPAM Systems  </div> <div style="font-weight:bold;">    6y 6m | Hyderabad | 18 Lacs    </div> </div> <div style="text-align:right">  <div>7731004321</div>   <div>mahesh96.kotha@gmail.com</div>  </div> <div style="width:100%; height:1px; background-color: #d6d6d6; margin-top: 5px"> </div> </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <span style="font-weight:bold;font-size:1.4em;">“</span> ReactJS Developer seeking roles in Dreamweaver, Javascript, React.Js, Frontend Development,UI Development,Web Development,Api Integration,Web Designing, Material Ui, Nextjs, Responsive Web Design. </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">WORK SUMMARY</div> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> Frontend/UI developer with 5.5+ years experience in building and
