* Responsible for creating the navigation menu and submenu
in the site using html, css, Javascript.  </div>   <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">PROJECT DETAILS</div>  <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">  <div style="color:#4E81BD;font-weight:bold;">DAZN LP</div>   <div style="color:#A6A6A5;">Jul '23 to till date</div>  </div> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">  <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Client : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">DAZN</span> </div>    <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Nature of Employment : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Full time</span> </div>     </div>  <div> <div style="font-weight:bold;">Project Details:</div> <div> The DAZN landing page project is designed to provide a seamless user experience for visitors landing on the DAZN website. This involves multiple functionalities, including user authentication, navigation, and dynamic content display. </div> </div>  </div>  <div style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">  <div style="color:#4E81BD;font-weight:bold;">E-commerce : Online hotel room booking system</div>   <div style="color:#A6A6A5;">Feb '21 to Jun '22</div>  </div> <div style="margin-bottom:15px;">  <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Client : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Bayat Hotels</span> </div>    <div style="clear: both;display: table;"> <label style="font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:3px;margin-right:15px;"><b>Nature of Employment : </b></label> <span style="display:inline-block;width:500px">Full time</span> </div>     </div>  <div> <div style="font-weight:bold;">Project Details:</div> <div> e-commerce website for online room booking system and integrated payment gateway - checkout </div> </div>  </div>   </div> <div style="margin-bottom:30px;">  <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">EDUCATION DETAILS</div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div>P.G.</div> <div> MCA (Computers)  2018 </div> <div>VR Siddharth Engineering College, Vijayawada</div> </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:15px;"> <div>U.G.</div> <div> B.Sc (Computers)  2015 </div> <div>DVR  Degree Collage, Nandigama</div> </div>    </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:30px;"> <div style="font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:10px;color:#F79647;">IT SKILLS</div> <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;color:#7F7F7F;"> <tr> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;"> Skill Name </th> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;"> Version </th> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;"> Last Used </th> <th style="text-align:left;padding:8px;background-color:#F6F6F6;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;"> Experience </th> </tr>  <tr> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">Javascript</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">Es6</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">2024</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">5y 6m</td> </tr>  <tr> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">HTML</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">5</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">2024</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">5y 6m</td> </tr>  <tr> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">CSS</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">3</td> <td style="padding:8px;border:1px solid #7F7F7F;">2024</td> <td style